      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·魯頌·003.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">泮水.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>明明魯侯，克明其德。既作泮宮，淮夷攸服。
矯矯虎臣，在泮獻馘。淑問如臯陶，在泮獻囚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>5. Very intelligent is the marquis of Lû,
Making his virtue illustrious.
He has made this college with its semicircle of water,
And the tribes of the Hwâi will submit to him.
His martial-looking tiger-leaders
Will here present the left ears (of their foes).
His examiners, wise as Kâo-yâo,
Will here present the prisoners.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-lusong-003__006__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">song-lusong-003</prop>
