      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·魯頌·003.7</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">泮水.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>角弓其觩，束矢其搜。戎車孔博，徒御無斁。
既克淮夷，孔淑不逆。式固爾猶，淮夷卒獲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>7. How they draw their bows adorned with bone!
How their arrows whiz forth!
Their war chariots are very large!
Their footmen and charioteers never weary!
They have subdued the tribes of Hwâi,
And brought them to an unrebellious submission.
Only lay your plans securely,
And all the tribes of the Hwâi will be won.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-lusong-003__008__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
